             was indicted for that <rs id="t18000528-15-off85" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000528-15-off85" type="offenceCategory" value="sexual"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000528-15-off85" type="offenceSubcategory" value="bigamy"></interp>
               she, on the <rs id="t18000528-15-cd86" type="crimeDate">20th of November, in the 39th year of his Majesty's reign</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000528-15-off85 t18000528-15-cd86"></join>, being then married to 
                     
                        <persName id="t18000528-15-victim211" type="victimName">
                           Joshua 
                           Ahier
